These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, mirinda, sprite
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, lizard, mouse, rat
4 different games are played: backgammon, whist, chess, mah-jongg
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing whist##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person drinking cola is the owner of the chinchilla##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the person playing chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage    | fanta  | sprite | mirinda    | cola       |
| Pet         | lizard | rat    | mouse      | chinchilla |
| Game   | backgammon   | chess | whist | mah-jongg        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-2::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, broccoli, corn, pear
There are 4 different favourite colors: turquise, pink, white, red
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person who likes red##1
2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who likes white is on the right of the person eating corn##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person driving the bike is the person who likes turquise##1
6. the person driving the roller is the person eating broccoli##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2     |       3       |     4     |
| Food        | corn   | broccoli | asparagus     | pear      |
| Color         | pink | white | red | turquise |
| Transport   | car    | roller   | motorbike     | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, rock-climbing, singing, video-games
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, electronic, hip-hop, pop
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, western, sports, musical
1. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
2. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the fan of hip-hop##1
5. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
6. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
7. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing | singing | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic    | country | hip-hop     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | sports    | musical | western    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, swisher, old-henry, cain
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, soccer, volleyball
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike, taxi, train
1. the old-henry-smoker is the person driving the train##1
2. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the train##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is rowing is the old-henry-smoker##1
7. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the cain-smoker is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |        2        |     3      |      4      |
| Cigar         | havana | cain | old-henry | swisher |
| Sport       | rugby     | volleyball      | rowing     | soccer      |
| Transport   | motorbike | jet-ski         | train      | taxi        |

