.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic, writer
There are 4 different nationalities: german, british, thai, indian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, trance
1. the accountant is the fan of funk##1
2. the fan of folk is on the right of the fan of trance##1
3. the german is on the right of the writer##1
4. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
5. the designer is on the far left##1
6. the thai is the mechanic##1
7. the fan of funk is on the right of the british##1
8. the writer is the fan of reggae##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | designer | mechanic | writer | accountant |
| Nationality   | indian   | thai  | british | german   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | folk     | reggae | funk       |

