.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, purple, blue, ebony
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, mouse, rabbit, turtle
1. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the turtle##1
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the person who likes blue is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
7. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | iced-tea | mirinda | 7up        |
| Color       | ebony | light-blue  | purple | blue     |
| Pet        | mouse    | rabbit   | turtle  | chinchilla |

