3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| City   | colone     | marseilles     | paris        | rome   |
| Sport         | sailing   | lacrosse | skateboarding | skiing  |

