3. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the roller is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the security-guard is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the software-developer is on the left of the security-guard##1
7. the bartender is on the far right##1
8. the indonesian is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Job   | designer   | software-developer  | security-guard    | bartender    |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | canadian  | indonesian |
| Transport     | roller  | helicopter | motorbike | car        |

