.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-16::.
House: tower, gothic-revival, modern, ranch-style
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, fantasy, superhero, thriller
4 different pets are kept: bird, fish, horse, rabbit
1. the ranch-style house is on the right of the tower house##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the gothic-revival house is the owner of the horse##1
5. the ranch-style house is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the modern house##1
7. the modern house is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| House          | tower     | ranch-style   | modern | gothic-revival |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | thriller | superhero | fantasy   |
| Pet           | rabbit    | fish     | bird      | horse     |

